# qickrapps.au — Project Rules & Architecture

## Overview
This repo is a **portfolio monorepo** that aggregates multiple sub-projects under the
`qickrapps.au` domain. The root hosts each sub-project as a top-level folder. A central
Astro 5 shell (`portfolio/`) serves as the public-facing hub at `qickrapps.au`.

