## Adding a New Project

1. Create a folder at the repo root: `my-new-project/`
2. Add `my-new-project/portfolio.manifest.json` (see schema below)
3. Register the folder name in `scripts/sync-manifests.js` → `SUB_PROJECTS` array
4. Push to `main` — GitHub Actions auto-syncs and redeploys

